F3 "" 0 0 50 H I C CNN
DRAW
P 2 0 1 0 -30 50 0 100 N
P 2 0 1 0 0 0 0 100 N
P 2 0 1 0 0 100 30 50 N
X +3V3 1 0 0 0 U 50 50 1 1 W N
ENDDRAW
ENDDEF
